column2: Enable 'Remove From Sphere' Decisions
The decisions to voluntarily remove countries from your Sphere of Influence are turned off by default (to keep them from cluttering up your list). Select this decision to enable them.
Disable 'Remove From Sphere' Decisions
This will disenable your 'Remove From Sphere' decisions, so they no longer clutter up your list.
